column2: SELECT   p.ra, p.g, p.r, p.i, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   (s.z BETWEEN # AND #)  AND (p.b > # OR p.b < #)  AND (p.g BETWEEN # AND #)   AND (p.r BETWEEN # AND #)   AND (p.i BETWEEN # AND #)   AND (s.class = &&& OR s.class = &&&)
